<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to PostApp</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        ul {
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #555;
        }
        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .button.sign-in {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
        }
        .button.sign-in:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .button.sign-up {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
        }
        .button.sign-up:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to PostApp</h1>
    <p>PostApp is your platform to share thoughts, connect with friends, and manage your posts seamlessly. Whether you want to share a story, update your followers, or chat with friends, PostApp has you covered.</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Like:</strong> Engage with posts by liking them to show your support.</li>
        <li><strong>Edit & Delete:</strong> Make changes to your posts or remove them anytime.</li>
        <li><strong>Chat with Friends:</strong> Connect with your friends and chat in real-time.</li>
        <li><strong>Follow Updates:</strong> Stay updated with the latest from your network.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Join PostApp today and start sharing your moments!</p>
    <div class="button-container">
        <a href="/login"><button class="button sign-in">Sign In</button></a>
        <a href="/create"><button class="button sign-up">Sign Up</button></a>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
